data.description: Perry homes exquisite 4 bed/3 bath home snuggled in a desirable Riverpark West subdivision. Exceptionally unique Ranch Style single-story floorplan consists of a master suite, a guest room w/full attached bath/closet, a French door study/library, a formal dining area, a huge family room adjoined with elegant gourmet kitchen and breakfast area, 2 additional bedrooms, full hallway bathroom, and an oversized utility room. The family area boasts soaring ceilings, elegant, tiled floors & stone accented fireplace. The gourmet oversized island kitchen has stainless steel appliances, a built-in microwave, a dishwasher & a gas cooktop. The countertops are beautiful granite accented by a tiled backsplash. Recent updates include tiles in all bedrooms and closets, a tiled standing shower in the guest bedroom, granite countertops in all bathrooms & a lot more (See Upgrades in the Documents section). The backyard includes an extended covered patio and two pergolas for extra shade and outdoor living.
